Package: funbootband
Title: Simultaneous Prediction and Confidence Bands for Functional Data
Version: 0.1.1
Authors@R: person("Daniel","Koska", email="dkoska@proton.me", role=c("aut","cre"), comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-8245-5222"))
Description: Computes simultaneous prediction and confidence bands for dense functional data,
    including hierarchical (clustered) designs via deterministic bootstrap resampling.
    Provides a simple API ('band()') and an Rcpp backend for performance.
License: GPL-3
URL: https://github.com/koda86/funbootband, https://koda86.github.io/funbootband/
BugReports: https://github.com/koda86/funbootband/issues
Depends: R (>= 3.5)
Imports: Rcpp, stats
LinkingTo: Rcpp
Suggests: testthat (>= 3.0.0), knitr, rmarkdown
VignetteBuilder: knitr
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
SystemRequirements: C++11
Config/testthat/edition: 3
ByteCompile: true
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
